{"tid":1017046,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"R/M字頭又有好野申請! 關愛基金助18萬戶換電視機頂盒","createTime":"2019-02-11T07:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T11:49:26.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4d72d65b5a132719aa93a7980249512ed779e6ec","tid":1017046,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T07:52:51.000Z","msg":"港府原定於2012年底，全面取消俗稱「雪花」電視的模擬電視廣播，騰出共160兆赫的頻譜，供室內流動電訊服務使用，惟押後多年後，終決定在明年12月起，終止模擬電視廣播。目前全港18萬受影響的模擬電視住戶，商經局初步建議他們，申請「關愛基金」撥款，購置數碼電視或機頂盒，預計約有16萬戶合資格申請。 <br />\n<br />\n美國、日本、英國和澳洲等地，早於2014年或之前，已終止模擬電視廣播。香港雖在2007年12月，已推行數碼電視廣播，但因要增加數碼頻道的用戶滲透率，毗鄰的廣東省最快亦要到2020年底，才取消模擬電視廣播。為免騰出的頻譜被內地干擾，港府遂兩度押後取消模擬電視廣播的期限。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190211/59246761\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190211%2F59246761&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu1z1D2OVAb2WcgpQnG2a6kfc%3D&h=0b983216\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190211%2F59246761&h=b0c8925f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190211/59246761</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> MAGIC TV正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可惜只有R/M字頭合資格"},{"pid":"01b3cdb92c738523fce209f6ba3b1fe234a4ec1e","tid":1017046,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T09:27:28.000Z","msg":"小米電視(中央人民電視台特供版)？"},{"pid":"11d090e700686053aa3049bb3c9f60df8e4da4d6","tid":1017046,"uid":124410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T11:49:26.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n換電視機都幫埋窮撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾時支助埋錢比人叫雞出火呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}